                            few kids have the opportunity to learn to program because it is rarely taught in
                            school.</br>
                            <strong><h1>Why Computer Science?</h1></strong></br>
                            Software is becoming a critical need of all our lives. It is the language of our world.
                            This year, almost 200 million students around the world were exposed to coding through the
                            Hour of Code event. And over 90% of parents want programming added to their child’s
                            curriculum.
                            We are seeking to apply the we code kids program in schools to create a fun and engaging
                            where children not only learn to program, but also have opportunities to be creative using
                            code.</br>


                            <canvas id="myChart"
                                    style="max-height:400px; max-width:400px; margin-left:20%; font-family: 'Menlo', 'Monaco', monospace"></canvas>

                            <script>
                                var ctx = document.getElementById("myChart").getContext("2d");
                                ctx.canvas.width = 50;
                                ctx.canvas.height = 50;

                                var myChart = new Chart(ctx, {
                                    type: 'pie',
                                    data: {
                                        labels: [
                                            "Parents want programming curriculum",
                                            "Others opinion"

                                        ],
                                        datasets: [
                                            {
                                                data: [90, 10],
                                                backgroundColor: [
                                                    "#373940",
                                                    "#18bc9c"

                                                ],
                                                hoverBackgroundColor: [
                                                    "#373940",
                                                    "#18bc9c"

                                                ]
                                            }]
                                    }
                                });
                            </script>

                            </br>
                            <strong><h1>Objective:</h1></strong>
                            <ul>

                                <li>Raise awareness about coding and bring coding into hundreds of schools .
                                </li>
                                <li>Empowering kids and gives them tools to express themselves in really cool way</li>
                                <li>Increase the number of programmers , over the next years</li>
                                <li>programming will be one of the fastest growing occupations Helping kids to thinks
                                    better, and create a best way of thinking about things in all domain .
                                </li>

                            </ul>

                            <strong><h1>Direct Goals:</h1></strong>
                            <ul>

                                <li>100 schools participate in the WeCode kids program during 5 years</li>
                                <li>2500 students</li>
                                <li>4500 training hours</li>


                            </ul>


